object: Returns the value of attribute object
name: Returns the value of attribute name
values: Returns the value of attribute values
column: Returns the value of attribute column
blank_date_parameter?:
Checks whether some blank date parameter exists. Note that this is different
than the validate_required_parameters! method, since it just checks for blank
positions instead of missing ones, and does not raise in case one blank position
exists. The caller is responsible to handle the case of this returning true.
validate_required_parameters!: If some position is not provided, it errors out a missing parameter exception.
